org.gvsig.gpe.prov.kml.writer.v2.features

Class DocumentWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.gpe.prov.kml.writer.v2.features.DocumentWriter

  • public class DocumentWriter
extends Object
    This class writes a Document kml tag. Example: 

     
 <Document>
 <Placemark>
 <name>CDATA example</name>
 <description>Description example</description>
 <Point>
 <oordinates>102.595626,14.996729</coordinates>
 </Point>
 </Placemark>
 </Document>

    See Also:
    http://code.google.com/apis/kml/documentation/kml_tags_21.html#document
